{"about_the_game":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CHAPTER 1</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Snow Melts</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a detective, who has been hired to discover the mysterious closure. Among various anomalies, find out what is happening to the park, why is it going bankrupt?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There's something pulling the park. Investigate what this thing is, and why it is there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It could be very dangerous for the future of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WELCOME TO JOLLY'S PARK</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will return to the old Jolly's Park, and discover the mystery of the close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will meet the mascots, but they might be... alive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GET YOUR JOLLY TABLET</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/JollyTabletGif.gif?t=1731690047\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>ATTENTION TO STAFF: ANY DAMAGE IS YOUR FAULT AND WILL BE DISCOUNTED ON YOUR FINAL CREDIT.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>JOLLY TABLET</strong> is really useful, but dangerous for the mascots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>UPGRADE YOUR JOLLY TABLET</strong></i></u> while you get into other sectors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>HACK THE GATES</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/JollyTabletTestGif.gif?t=1731690047\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>ATTENTION: DO NOT USE THIS TO GET INTO RESTRICTED AREAS.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hack gates to access other sectors, and, in an ambuscade, it is EXTREMELY IMPORTANT to get in other rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You don't want to be devoured, right?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>And really important: Avoid WALLY</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/WallyChaseGif.gif?t=1731690047\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet Wally, Berry, Whootie, Max, Jolly and others. They are not that scary, right? Just take care, they are seeing you everywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore abandonado attractions. Resolve puzzles, your Jolly Tablet is really useful, not? Contact your allies using it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">MATURE CONTENT WARNING:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Violence, fear,\u00a0inappropriate language.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Forgot my Tickets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3289600/5495eae148e590c424dc3dcd76fc5a121418214c.jpg"},{"name":"Lights On","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3289600/45e229d1f584eecef4658edb804b7c84c592f59b.jpg"},{"name":"I Can See You","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3289600/77031c073ed87b827691995d38bb8bad1795fb4c.jpg"},{"name":"Ouch!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3289600/e9ba8aba535359114f796f9f663e9643fd87e111.jpg"},{"name":"Hey, you forgot your claw!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3289600/cd970d852538cdb926f92f8702e2f6bcd7b6de61.jpg"},{"name":"Alive Penguin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap